### Uni Pilot API - Onboarding Tests
### Run these after authentication tests (requires valid token)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiVersion = v1

### Use token from login (you'll need to copy it from 01-auth.http response)
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get All Universities
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/universities
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get Universities with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/universities?search=Berlin
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get Universities with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/universities?limit=10&offset=0
Accept: application/json

### 4. Get Study Programs by University ID (replace {id} with actual university ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/universities/1/study-programs
Accept: application/json

### 5. Get Study Programs by University ID - Filter by Degree Type
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/universities/1/study-programs?degree_type=Bachelor
Accept: application/json

### 6. Get Career Tree for Study Program (replace {id} with actual study program ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/study-programs/1/career-tree
Accept: application/json

### 7. Get All Topic Fields
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/topic-fields
Accept: application/json

### 8. Get Topic Fields with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/topic-fields?search=Full Stack
Accept: application/json

### 9. Get Topic Field by ID (replace {id} with actual topic field ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/topic-fields/1
Accept: application/json

### 10. Select Topic Field for User (requires authentication)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users/me/profile/topic-field
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic_field_id": 1
}

### 11. Create User Question (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users/me/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question_text": "Are you interested in frontend development?",
  "answer": true,
  "career_tree_node_id": 1
}

### 12. Create User Question - Without Career Tree Node
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users/me/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question_text": "Do you prefer working in teams?",
  "answer": true
}

### 13. Get User Questions (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users/me/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 14. Get User Questions - Filtered by Career Tree Node
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users/me/questions?career_tree_node_id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

